---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { siteConfig } from '../site.config';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy policy for Class Action News & Settlements.">
  <section class="bg-white py-12 lg:py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-black text-gray-900 mb-2">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <div class="prose-article">
        <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>{siteConfig.name} ("we," "us," or "our") collects information you provide directly, such as your name, email address, state of residence, and topics of interest when you sign up for alerts or submit forms on our site.</p>
        <p>We also automatically collect certain technical information when you visit our site, including your IP address, browser type, pages visited, and referring URL. This data is collected through analytics tools to help us understand how our site is used.</p>

        <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information we collect to send you class action settlement alerts and news updates you've subscribed to, respond to your inquiries and form submissions, improve our website and services, and analyze site traffic and user behavior in aggregate.</p>

        <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with service providers who help us operate our site (email delivery, analytics), and when required by law or legal process. If you submit an inquiry through our Attorney Portal, your contact information will be shared with relevant legal partners.</p>

        <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
        <p>We use cookies and similar technologies to analyze site traffic through Google Analytics, measure advertising effectiveness, and remember your preferences. You can control cookie settings through your browser.</p>

        <h2>Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You may unsubscribe from our email communications at any time by clicking the "unsubscribe" link in any email. To request deletion of your personal information, contact us at the address below.</p>

        <h2>Contact Us</h2>
        <p>{siteConfig.name}<br />{siteConfig.contact.address}<br />{siteConfig.contact.city}, {siteConfig.contact.state} {siteConfig.contact.zip}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
